<lb ed="B" n="0895b14"/>也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>黧</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0895b1403" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">良脂切黑色也</note></p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>趼</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pB25p0895b1410" style="margin-left:1em" cb:place="inline"><note place="inline">吉典切足胝也</note></p></cb:def></entry></cb:div>
